27:09.497 --> 27:11.107
Put this on.

27:21.640 --> 27:24.033
Turn around,
and get on your knees, agent.

27:40.180 --> 27:44.401
I don't kill anyone
I don't have to.
Let's keep it that way.

27:44.401 --> 27:46.229
You don't have to.

27:47.927 --> 27:49.711
You don't have
to kill anyone else.

27:49.711 --> 27:53.367
I'll be judge of that.
On the ground.

28:03.246 --> 28:04.465
Count to 100.

28:08.556 --> 28:09.383
One,

28:11.777 --> 28:12.603
two,

28:14.605 --> 28:15.432
three,

28:17.304 --> 28:18.131
four,

28:20.611 --> 28:21.438
five,

28:24.093 --> 28:24.877
six,

28:27.618 --> 28:28.532
seven...

28:30.665 --> 28:33.624
Nick. It's Crown.
You hurt?

28:33.624 --> 28:35.801
I'm not.
Okay, he's close!
Fan out!

28:35.801 --> 28:37.280
AGENTS:
Go, go, go, go, go!

28:39.674 --> 28:40.806
No, come on!

28:42.677 --> 28:43.678
Go, go, go!

28:45.680 --> 28:47.682
