no questions asked.

33:01.109 --> 33:04.199
Your experience in that region
and with people in that world

33:04.199 --> 33:06.114
is invaluable to us, Isaac.

33:06.114 --> 33:08.987
So, given that and your
knowledge and understanding
of Rex Wolfe,

33:08.987 --> 33:10.205
this is now your case.

33:11.728 --> 33:13.556
Good.

33:13.556 --> 33:17.560
You'll go in dark to Moldova,
find Rex Wolfe,
and capture him.

33:17.560 --> 33:19.084
And then he'll go
to a black site.

33:19.084 --> 33:22.304
Yes. As far as
the American public
are concerned,

33:22.304 --> 33:23.653
Rex Wolfe does not exist.

33:25.829 --> 33:27.266
I'm taking Byrne with me.

33:29.485 --> 33:31.357
I trust her instincts.

33:35.491 --> 33:38.059
Byrne? You on board?

33:39.104 --> 33:39.930
Yeah.

33:41.019 --> 33:43.282
Okay. Any questions?

33:45.458 --> 33:47.851
Durand?

33:47.851 --> 33:52.421
Sir, I... I think
this is the right team
for the job.

33:54.728 --> 33:55.772
